  "markdown_content": "\n## Executive Summary\n\nManus completed the final deployment and testing of a comprehensive spiritual library platform for Yannick and Roberta. The platform now features fully functional PDF downloads, integrated payment system (€9/month subscription, €15 individual purchases), 3D interactive books, multilingual support (FR/IT/EN), and all identified issues have been resolved. The platform is now live at https://pkzqwtmx.manus.space and ready for commercial launch.\n\n\n## Context & Intent\n\nContinuation of a spiritual library platform development project, focusing on final corrections and deployment to make the platform commercially viable.\n\n\n## What Was Done\n\nFixed all previously identified issues including PDF download functionality, payment system integration, footer navigation, spiritual progression paths, 3D book visualization, author photo integration, and responsive design optimization. Successfully deployed the complete platform to public network.\n\n\n## Outputs Produced\n\n- [web_platform] Spiritual Library Website — Complete multilingual spiritual library platform with e-commerce capabilities\n- [pdf_content] Spiritual Booklets — 20+ page authentic PDF booklets for each spiritual category\n- [deployment] Live Platform — Deployed platform at https://pkzqwtmx.manus.space\n\n## Key Decisions & Validations\n\n- Set test pricing at €0 for platform validation\n- Implemented progressive spiritual paths with 4 levels\n- Integrated 3D book visualization with QR codes\n- Established subscription model at €9/month with €15 individual purchases\n\n## Lessons Learned\n\nWorked well:\n\n- Context inheritance for task continuity\n- Comprehensive testing before declaring completion\n- Integration of visual and functional elements\nDiscoveries:\n\n- Platform achieved professional-grade functionality across all requirements\n\n## Next Steps\n\n- Monitor platform performance post-launch\n- Gather user feedback for iterative improvements\n- Scale content library based on user engagement\n---\nUID: MzqGcKCGGQBDk6zFUI03ZP | Model: claude-sonnet-4-20250514 | Cost: $0.0156\n"
}